snippet.title: Quick Vid- Grimaces Birthday Gameplay
snippet.description:
Expect a good review later today!

The Grimace’s Birthday game was an honest meh, art is amazing, but I accidentally chose hard mode which turned off the auto grinding, lol, so 7/10 and then a full gameplay on normal mode :)
